{"tid":1489052,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我支持塞鐵 你們可以屌我了","createTime":"2019-08-19T18:55:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T15:27:16.000Z","uid":209526,"like":25,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"311c33cc93d9cac213c9ac2336242bdd488adc92","tid":1489052,"uid":209526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:55:37.000Z","msg":"每次逢要準備塞鐵成日就會有班所謂既「<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我睇通曬全局既軍師</span></span></strong>」出黎<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反塞鐵</span></span>，又屌呢樣又屌果樣，仲開谷話要拉班人走。但唔該你地班人同我擘大你個屎眼同我睇清楚，塞鐵既用處同效益你地到底有冇睇透過。<br />\n遊行示威行左幾多次，前日170萬人再出黎，政府都係繼續白內障，咩都唔回應。勇武前線700個比人拉左。<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>連機場都比人出埋禁制令，佢出得一次可以有第二次，第三次</strong></span></span>，唔係話機場冇用，而係你睇下每次要幾多人先至可以癱瘓機場，<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">第二日繼續就已經又少一堆</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">重點</span></strong></span>係，一個月前<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>7.21冇人唔記得</strong></span>，你同我講要幫佢地<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>討回公道</strong></span>。結果你同我講，繼續坐啦，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">坐坐下政府就會開竅</span></span></strong>，會出黎回應。唔好傻啦，你唔升級都連班「真。打工仔」，商家佬都噪政府，我地邊夠籌碼去談判？<br />\n<br />\n而唯一你唔洗驚會比人用車撞，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非既抗爭升級方式就係升級不合作運動</span></span></strong>，由<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">8.21</span></strong></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">開始，荔景，九龍塘，炮台山</span></span></strong>塞9死地鐵呢個命脈。再唔回應訴求，之後<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">每日塞，塞曬全線，塞到林病怕為止</span></strong>。<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">如果連呢種犧牲同覺悟都做唔到，香港人唔好同我出黎講抗爭</span></strong>。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iGzbvoG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiGzbvoG.jpg&h=2adb6570&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n谷LINK:  <a href=\"https://t.me/mtrisdangerous\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmtrisdangerous&d=OqNKNX3jJWm7Bjx4wMOexwEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=97e846bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/mtrisdangerous</a>"},{"pid":"a19c65cfb8d65ae42e3e4ccd19ca96961c3929c6","tid":1489052,"uid":209526,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:56:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DP1Utz5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDP1Utz5.jpg&h=d546c1fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20a3736f2f56493d4c3c5bc37195fa7e52403975","tid":1489052,"uid":209526,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:56:55.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"f33b5c63f6cb2acf922c70f2b9b60fba65ff997f","tid":1489052,"uid":209526,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:57:05.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"862ccb54b47ae2c9dc8fdd64afd266706df62e83","tid":1489052,"uid":209526,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:57:15.000Z","msg":"自推3"},{"pid":"95379cccc2d3359e4dda5ce7259a6efcfa10e640","tid":1489052,"uid":209526,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:57:26.000Z","msg":"自推4"},{"pid":"e85c11965d459154fcaae4a6c153153613304d4e","tid":1489052,"uid":209526,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:57:36.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"90329327ad05841b8fa41be29f6470e3711ff422","tid":1489052,"uid":209526,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:57:48.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"36a60d5e0afffe9171c365d9a253f09d67ae55a8","tid":1489052,"uid":209526,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:57:58.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"45ddda9188f3639a4ec950bd81959a0f20c5070e","tid":1489052,"uid":209526,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:58:08.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"2c5a16a025caace