,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T19:40:00.000Z","msg":"唔係話塞機場唔值得做<br />\n<br />\n而係每個行動都有佢既限制同影響<br />\n上星期兩日機場大家見到結果<br />\n有人話塞機場無塞鐵咁失民意<br />\n結果就偏偏打左呢個說法一大巴<br />\n<br />\n所以各有各做啦"},{"pid":"5e68801553c946413712dcee047e917a12b3ba31","tid":1489052,"uid":277084,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"95f96f54fd3d6b40c00017fe10179ab4d6b6219c","tid":1489052,"uid":273760,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c65a64cbe2eeebe57d1b920361181eb3636dab5e","tid":1489052,"uid":209526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ba2634eab6db1bfe2ea54ae1a4a6e2576ed69b33","tid":1489052,"uid":11698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T19:12:59.000Z","msg":"要塞去塞機場啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T19:16:14.000Z","msg":"各有各做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T19:32:24.000Z","msg":"冷靜d啦<br />\n依家贏緊5:0<br />\n最緊要集氣係831同9月9阿<br />\n依家中間既過程可以勇武流水式<br />\n但係搞果班人好多都係你支持者<br />\n林鄭最想要果張牌就係你塞地鐵<br />\n唔好送牌比林鄭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T19:41:47.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"48ea0b61f9e70b95c70b95472bb82662bb4e526f","tid":1489052,"uid":105358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T19:49:58.000Z","msg":"如果民意冇用點解做文宣，點解唔搞突撃影響仲大<br />\n如果向港鐵施壓，點解唔搞入閘機，冇市民會屌"},{"pid":"7f43f08e2d7a96f3e7fd0d2dd7a5fa47a679280e","tid":1489052,"uid":40170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"48ea0b61f9e70b95c70b95472bb82662bb4e526f","tid":1489052,"uid":105358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T19:49:58.000Z","msg":"如果民意冇用點解做文宣，點解唔搞突撃影響仲大<br />\n如果向港鐵施壓，點解唔搞入閘機，冇市民會屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T19:53:44.000Z","msg":"你估出閘嗰陣佢地屌唔屌<br />\n又無車飛 又要排隊搵minions<br />\n<br />\n而家係不合作運動 唔係超合作運動<br />\n你超合作爭取咗幾十字回覆啦<br />\n排隊到不合作未？"},{"pid":"d000c26400d39c6d740632b7784304af2012b80e","tid":1489052,"uid":147345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedB